(4730, 887, 'why_vsms', 'Major strengths of VSMS are the dynamic, highly committed and visionary management; the state –of-the art infrastructure and well qualified, experienced and very dedicated faculty with diverse academic and industrial background. Among all the B. Schools of Kerala VSMS has the largest number of publications authored by the faculty. A number book of the faculty of VSMS is recommended by Universities and Institutes throughout India for a variety of courses. Several of them are recommended by AICTE and UGC for various courses.'),
