(5828, 1163, 'mission', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled list-arw\">\r\n 	<li>We commit to develop the institution as a Center of Excellence of International Standards</li>\r\n 	<li>We guide our students in the attainment of intellectual and professional competence for successfully coping with the rapid advancements in technologies and the ever changing world of business, industry and services</li>\r\n 	<li>We help each and every student in their personal growth into mature and responsible individuals</li>\r\n 	<li>We strive to cultivate a sense of social and civic responsibility in our students, thus empowering them to serve the humanity</li>\r\n 	<li>We promise to ensure a free environment where quest for the truth is encouraged</li>\r\n</ul>'),
