(5840, 1166, 'project_in_the_area_of_specialisation', '<h4>Evaluation is based on the following:-\r\nTwo progress assessments 20%\r\nFinal Project Report 30%\r\nProject presentation and Viva-voce 50%</h4>\r\nIf the project work is not completed satisfactorily, the student has to work further and again appear for assessment on a specified date, not earlier than two weeks after the first evaluation.'),
