(5878, 1174, 'points', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled list-arw\">\r\n 	<li>Systematic and Accurate calendar: KTU being a university focusing on improving student life during academic sessions, provides an accurate and systematic calendar with details regarding Semester start and end dates, dates of various internal semester examinations, induction course dates, supplementary exam dates, dates for activities enabling affiliate Institutes to plan ahead and make student academic life a peaceful one</li>\r\n 	<li>Timely and prompt completion of course and announcement of results.</li>\r\n 	<li>Course Syllabus are closely related to Industry and Commerce and are regularly updated.</li>\r\n 	<li>Better Placement opportunities for students as a result of a competitive syllabus and timely announcement of results</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled list-arw\">\r\n 	<li>A wider range of functional areas can be opted by the student as their elective subjects giving them a competitive edge in the job market. Some of the vital elective areas are Finance, Marketing, HR, IT, Operations Management, Logistics Management, International Business etc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Making academics an enjoyable and interesting learning process by offering students a wide range of areas of study relevant to the industry and job markets.</li>\r\n 	<li>Foundation Courses: Foundation course comprising of Accounting, Statistics, Economics and Principles of Management and Computer Application makes a comfortable learning platform for students coming from non commerce backgrounds like Engineering, Sciences and Arts.</li>\r\n 	<li>As in International Universities Students may opt for self study courses to suit their interest and ability and secure Certificates from the University.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
