(71, 1, '2019-02-25 10:32:40', '2019-02-25 10:32:40', 'A one-day training session led by Prof. Vivek (Management Academician from Muscat) was\r\norganized for the Tl MBA students. The Chief Resource person conveyed to the students that\r\nthey should \'Take the road that is less traveled\', as he felt that was the key to success.\r\n\r\nThe session witnessed several team building activities and problem-solving activities for the\r\nstudents. It was a refreshing event which allowed students to take a short break from the usual\r\nacademic course of studies.', 'One day Training on \'Enhancing Aspirations\' by Prof. Vivek', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'upcoming-events', '', '', '2019-03-19 11:03:18', '2019-03-19 11:03:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?p=71', 0, 'post', '', 0),
