(78, 1, '2019-02-25 10:37:51', '2019-02-25 10:37:51', '<p class=\"animated fadeInUp , anim1\">VISWAJYOTHI&nbsp; provides excellent hostel facilities for students. Gent’s hostel is located in the campus itself so it makes easy access between college&nbsp;&nbsp;and students. The hostels and hostel facilities are of high quality and well equipped. The boys hostel can accommodate 250 boys. Members of the teaching staff are appointed as Resident Tutors in the hostel. The rooms provide most modern facilities and privacy &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"animated fadeInUp , anim1\">The hostel system runs under the control of chief warden Rev.Fr. Thomas Kottaram and resident tutors. All the hostels have mess facilities for students. The mess is spacious, highly hygienic and elegant.Internet&nbsp;&nbsp; and Computer Facilities are&nbsp;&nbsp; also available in the hostel.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"animated fadeInUp , anim1\"><span id=\"lblladiesHostel\">The Gents Hostel is located inside the campus. The Hostel has a capacity of 357 beds.</span></p>', 'Hostel Life', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'campus-life-2', '', '', '2019-03-26 11:44:59', '2019-03-26 11:44:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?post_type=lfevsms&#038;p=78', 0, 'lfevsms', '', 0),
(79, 1, '2019-02-25 10:37:57', '2019-02-25 10:37:57', '<p class=\"animated fadeInUp , anim1\">VISWAJYOTHI has a Multi Gym with all most modern equipments. Students and staffs are using this facility to keep their health in good condition. Staffs and students can utilize the Gym facility in the early morning and evening times.</p>\r\n<p class=\"animated fadeInUp , anim1\">VISWAJYOTHI has a Multi Gym with all most modern equipments. Students and staffs are using this facility to keep their health in good condition. Staffs and students can utilize the Gym facility in the early morning and evening times.</p>', 'Fitness Center', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fitness-center', '', '', '2019-03-26 11:44:12', '2019-03-26 11:44:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?post_type=lfevsms&#038;p=79', 0, 'lfevsms', '', 0),
(80, 1, '2019-02-25 10:38:02', '2019-02-25 10:38:02', '<article>\r\n<p class=\"animated fadeInUp , anim1\">VISWAJYOTHI is providing high class facilities for Sports and Games. Every year Annual Sports is being conducted in the college. We are giving equal preference to sports and games along with the academic activities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"animated fadeInUp , anim1\">VISWAJYOTHI has well trained professional basket ball team. Every year VISWAJYOTHI is conducting all kerala Basket Ball tournament “MAGNUM” in the mid of February. We also won many titles in various basket ball tournaments. VISWAJYOTHI is maintaining a Multi propose stadium with 200 Meter track as well as a Football and Cricket ground. Many football as well as cricket tournaments are held n this stadium. The college has 9 badminton courts (4 indoor and 5 outdoor) where students and staffs are practicing daily.</p>\r\n\r\n</article>', 'Sports Facilities', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sports-facilities', '', '', '2019-03-26 11:42:34', '2019-03-26 11:42:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?post_type=lfevsms&#038;p=80', 0, 'lfevsms', '', 0),
