(200, 1, '2019-02-27 08:57:08', '2019-02-27 08:57:08', 'The students can select elective courses from the list of elective courses offered for the programme. Specialization depends on the number of electives opted by the student in a specific area. Students will have to opt for four elective courses in the fourth trimester, four electives in the fifth trimester and two electives in the sixth trimester.\r\nThe students will have the option of auditing additional courses in any one of the specializations. Audited courses will not be considered for computing the CGPA.', 'CURRICULUM', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'curriculum', '', '', '2019-03-29 10:11:35', '2019-03-29 10:11:35', '', 131, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?page_id=200', 0, 'page', '', 0),
