(248, 1, '2019-02-27 11:56:22', '2019-02-27 11:56:22', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled list-arw\">\r\n 	<li>The One-time Application Fee of Rs 500 is to be paid at the time of submitting the Application Form.</li>\r\n 	<li>Admission Fee (one-time) of Rs.500 and a part of Tuition Fee Rs. 25,000 are to be paid together once admission is offered to the candidate. Thus, a candidate who has been offered admission will have to pay Rs. 25,500/-.\r\nTuition Fee for subsequent trimester will only be payable later.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'FEE STRUCTURE', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fee-structure', '', '', '2019-03-29 10:13:31', '2019-03-29 10:13:31', '', 15, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?page_id=248', 0, 'page', '', 0),
