(250, 1, '2019-02-27 11:57:03', '2019-02-27 11:57:03', 'The Second KMAT Kerala Entrance Examination for admission to MBA course for the academic year 2019-20 is proposed to be conducted on June 16, 2019 by Cochin University of Science and Technology (CUSAT) under the supervision of Admission Supervisory Committee (ASC). Aspiring candidates may apply online through the website <a href=\"https://kmatkerala.in\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://kmatkerala.in</a> from 5th march 2019 5.00 PM onwards. The last date for submitting online application is 31.05.2019, 4.00 PM. The application fee prescribed for general candidate is Rs 1000/- and Rs 750/- for SC/ST Candidate.\r\n\r\n<strong>Those who are studying for last year degree course and are awaiting their results may also apply for the KMAT KERALA Entrance Examination 2019.</strong>', 'NOTIFICATIONS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kmat-notifications', '', '', '2019-03-29 10:13:42', '2019-03-29 10:13:42', '', 15, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?page_id=250', 0, 'page', '', 0),
