(299, 1, '2019-02-28 05:54:27', '2019-02-28 05:54:27', '<h4>BODHI</h4>\r\nBodhi is an inter-collegiate techno management fest of VISWAJYOTHI, which has been hosted by the college ever since its inception in 2006. Bodhi has competitive events for engineers and management students. Bodhi opens up opportunity to test the mettle with the peers in colleges all over Kerala. Foot falls for the event is kept crawling up year after year. The event is conducted over a 3 days in the month of March.\r\n<h4>DRISHYA</h4>\r\nDrishya is an annual inter-college cultural fest organized by the students of VISWAJYOTHI. Drishya blends a series of fine-arts, socio-cultural and literary events, along with a variety of workshops, exhibitions and informal events. The fest attracts thousands of visitors to the campus annually, and is one of the biggest cultural fests in central kerala.', 'COLLEGE FEST', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'college-fest', '', '', '2019-03-29 10:16:02', '2019-03-29 10:16:02', '', 12, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?page_id=299', 0, 'page', '', 0),
