(343, 1, '2019-03-01 06:07:34', '2019-03-01 06:07:34', 'The biggest challengein front of a student is to choose the best. We endeavour to provide thebest and to bring out what is best in our students. We strive to combinejudiciously use of technology and moral values, employability and equity in thetransformation of young minds. Already into the thirteenth year of excellenceand continuing its pursuit of betterment VISWAJYOTHI College of Engineering andTechnology has earned a niche for itself in the engineering educational sectorin the country. An amazing response of students from the very inception,consistent result with university ranks, state of the art infrastructure,quality faculty members, impetus given to research and development, campusrecruitment and placement record, mentoring for students, sprawling campus and various student services ensure our credibility over theyears.', 'DIRECTOR MESSAGE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '180-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-01 06:07:34', '2019-03-01 06:07:34', '', 180, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/index.php/2019/03/01/180-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
