(346, 1, '2019-03-01 06:08:58', '2019-03-01 06:08:58', 'VISWAJYOTHI was established with the aim of imparting quality professional education to aspiring students. It persistently seeks and adopts innovative methods to improve the quality of higher education on a consistent basis.\r\nThe college believes in “ Moulding Engineers and Managers par Excellence with Integrity Fairness and Human Values “ and keeping this watch word in mind, the experienced and learned teachers are strongly encouraged to nurture the students. The high watermark set at VJCET in the field of teaching and research spurs us on in our relentless pursuit of excellence. The highly motivated students teamed with their bubbling energy ensure that the flag of VJCET soars high.', 'MANAGER MESSAGE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '178-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-01 06:08:58', '2019-03-01 06:08:58', '', 178, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/index.php/2019/03/01/178-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(347, 1, '2019-03-01 06:10:01', '2019-03-01 06:10:01', 'VISWAJYOTHI College of Engineering &amp; Technology, Vazhakulam can boast of producing competent engineers capable of facing the challenges in the technical field with zeal to social commitment and ethical values. Started only thirteen years back, our institution commands a formidable position amongst the various engineering colleges. This is achieved by excellent infrastructural facilities combined with the team work of enthusiastic management, dedicated faculty members,committed laboratory &amp; workshop staff members, sincere administrative staff members, motivating alumni and dynamic students. Excellent track records in the University examinations and the considerable number of placements reveal the effective co-ordination of all these resources. This is not an end in itself.We are striving hard to make the vision of the institution “Moulding Engineers par Excellence with integrity, fairness and human values” a reality.', 'PRINCIPAL MESSAGE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '181-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-03-01 06:10:01', '2019-03-01 06:10:01', '', 181, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/index.php/2019/03/01/181-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
