(595, 1, '2019-03-08 10:00:07', '2019-03-08 10:00:07', 'VISWAJYOTHI is providing high class facilities for Sports and Games. Every year Annual Sports is being conducted in the college. We are giving equal preference to sports and games along with the academic activities.\r\n\r\nVISWAJYOTHI has well trained professional basket ball team. Every year VISWAJYOTHI is conducting all kerala Basket Ball tournament “MAGNUM” in the mid of February. We also won many titles in various basket ball tournaments. VISWAJYOTHI is maintaining a Multi propose stadium with 200 Meter track as well as a Football and Cricket ground. Many football as well as cricket tournaments are held n this stadium. The college has 9 badminton courts (4 indoor and 5 outdoor) where students and staffs are practicing daily.', 'SPORTS FACILITIES', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sports-facilities', '', '', '2019-03-29 10:36:46', '2019-03-29 10:36:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/?post_type=campusfacility&#038;p=595', 0, 'campusfacility', '', 0),
