 K.E College, Mannanam, 2015</li>\r\n 	<li>Two Day National Seminar on Kerala Model of Development: Prospects and Challenges organized by the Department of Economics, Ettumanoorappan College Ettumanoor on 6<sup>th</sup> &amp; 7<sup>th</sup> March 2019.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><em> </em><strong>Professional Society Memberships</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lifetime member, Kerala Economic Association</li>\r\n 	<li>Lifetime member, Economics for Health and Educational Growth, New Delhi</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong> </strong><strong>POSITIONS HELD FOR THE LAST 10 YEARS  </strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>NSS Programme Officer K E College Mannanam</li>\r\n 	<li>Director, Economics Association K E College Mannanam</li>\r\n 	<li>Director College Arts Club K E College Mannanam</li>\r\n 	<li>Convener, Cultural Committee for Golden Jubilee Celebration of K E College Mannanam</li>\r\n 	<li>Teacher Coordinator College Tourism Club K E College</li>\r\n 	<li>Mannanam Director College Music Club K E College Mannanam</li>\r\n 	<li>Director Civil Service Coaching Centre, K E College Mannanam</li>\r\n 	<li>Chief Editor, New Numbers and Letters, A Refereed Research Journal Published by Kuriakose Elias College Mannanam</li>\r\n 	<li>President, K.E College Staff Co-operative Society Ltd. No K. 361</li>\r\n 	<li>Secretary, K.E College Staff Co-operative Society Ltd. No K. 361</li>\r\n 	<li>Member of Expert Committee for the revaluation, M A Economics M G University</li>\r\n 	<li>Member of Inspection Commission for assessing the infrastructural and instructional facilities to start new courses in various colleges affiliated to M G University, Kottayam.</li>\r\n 	<li>Member UG Economics Board of Studies, M G University Kottayam</li>\r\n 	<li>Member UG Economics Board of Studies, CMS College (Autonomous)</li>\r\n 	<li>Member Academic Council S H College (Autonomous) Thevara, Cochin</li>\r\n 	<li>Member Core Committee for restructuring Economies UG and PG Syllabus, M G University, Kottayam.</li>