(649, 1, '2019-03-09 11:24:48', '2019-03-09 11:24:48', 'The KMAT KERALA June 2018 entrance examination was proposed to conduct on 24.06.2018 but due to the present Nipah Virus issue in Kozhikode and Malappuram districts, the Government has postponed all the examinations and Government Programs. Therefore, the Hon’ble Chairman of ASC has discussed the matter with Dr. Chandrasekhar who is the Convener of the KMAT Kerala entrance examination 2018 on 05.06.2018 in the chamber of the Hon’ble Chairman.\r\n\r\n<strong>In the discussion held on 05.06.2018 Dr. Chandrasekhar also opined that it is better to postpone the KMAT Kerala entrance examination from June 24th and the same shall be conducted on 08.07.2018. <span class=\"none\">Since the issue is still persisting, it is decided that KMAT Kerala entrance examination scheduled on 24.06.2018 is postponed to 08.07.2018.</span> The below table shows the new time schedule for Entrance Examination on 08.07.2018.\r\nIn the event of postponement of the entrance exam. The date of commencement of Academic Session shall also be shifted to <span class=\"none\">8th August 2018</span> and the last date of closing of admission will be <span class=\"none\">15.08.2018.</span></strong>', 'NOTIFICATIONS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '250-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-09 11:24:48', '2019-03-09 11:24:48', '', 250, 'http://localhost/viswajyothi/viswawp/250-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(650, 1, '2019-03-11 06:17:33', '2019-03-11 06:17:33', 'Dear all,\r\n\r\nI feel so blessed to have an opportunity to share a few words with you all. I am enjoying every bit of my life. Not only do I grow professionally, but every day I experience renewed energy and personal growth.\r\n\r\nVISWAJYOTHI School of Management Studies is a unique institute which allows students to blossom by empowering them to take decisions at a very young age. It truly brings the entrepreneur out in a student and that helps them become great managers. It is an institute driven and run largely by the students themselves, which gives them a unique management experience that no text book can teach. It has a unique combination of excellent faculty &amp; a brilliant location that enables it to interact.\r\n\r\nI am very glad to be a part of the alumni association &amp; I extend my heartfelt support &amp; co-operation to make it a great success.', 'ClintJoy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'clintjoy', '', '', '2019-03-14 10:36:16', '2019-03-14 10:36:16', '', 0, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/?post_type=testimon&#038;p=650', 0, 'testimon', '', 0),
