(652, 1, '2019-03-11 06:32:59', '2019-03-11 06:32:59', 'VISWAJYOTHI School of Management Studies offers a blend of learning, amusement and integration of enduring principles. As a business administration student institution provides a wide arena and the student gets to learn something new with every subject. The environment not only helped me in imbibing knowledge but also in developing my over all personality, fuelling confidence in me. VISWAJYOTHI has achieved high quality education with prime focus on holistic learning and inculcating competitive abilities in students which has helped us immensely. The entire study environment makes it easy for a student to learn and inculcate the spirit to stand out amongst the talented and hardworking student. What amazed me is the plethora of extracurricular activities that the institute offers hence compelling every student to explore and pursue his or her extra talents. My sincere thanks to all the faculty members, mentors, and everyone in VSMS for their support and altruism. They have played a crucial role shaping me and proved me right in selecting VISWAJYOTHI over other colleges.', 'JacobJoy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jacobjoy', '', '', '2019-03-14 10:38:48', '2019-03-14 10:38:48', '', 0, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/?post_type=testimon&#038;p=652', 0, 'testimon', '', 0),
(653, 1, '2019-03-11 06:34:13', '2019-03-11 06:34:13', 'It’s my greatest blessing to share a few words with all regarding my college days at VISWAJYOTHI School of Management Studies. I feel privileged and honored to be a part of such an esteemed organisation where each one of the students gets an opportunity to grow and discover themselves. The highly skilled and knowledgeable faculty members enable the student to grab opportunities and take decisions to achieve heights in their life. The infrastructure and environment provided by the institute for the students are highly eminent. I am very glad to be a part of the alumni association &amp;amp; I extend my heartfelt support and co-operation to make it a great success.', 'SUSAN MARYJOHN', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'susan-maryjohn', '', '', '2019-03-14 10:33:16', '2019-03-14 10:33:16', '', 0, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/?post_type=testimon&#038;p=653', 0, 'testimon', '', 0),
(654, 1, '2019-03-11 06:57:33', '2019-03-11 06:57:33', 'VISWAJYOTHI was established with the aim of imparting quality professional education to aspiring students. It persistently seeks and adopts innovative methods to improve the quality of higher education on a consistent basis.\r\nThe college believes in “ Moulding Engineers and Managers par Excellence with Integrity Fairness and Human Values “ and keeping this watch word in mind, the experienced and learned teachers are strongly encouraged to nurture the students. The high watermark set at VJCET in the field of teaching and research spurs us on in our relentless pursuit of excellence. The highly motivated students teamed with their bubbling energy ensure that the flag of VJCET soars high.\r\n\r\nOur Alumni who have been placed at respectable posts in MNCs around the world have done us proud. We have been able to maintain the ties with a number of respectable MNCs which aid our placement.\r\n\r\nVJCET essentially has excellent infrastructure, ambience conducive to learning, well equipped laboratories and workshops, comfortable hostels for gents and ladies, state-of-art-library and loads of other facilities.\r\n\r\nWe have been serving the society for the past ten years and with steady steps and we continue our march forward. We look forward to meeting you at VJCET.', 'MANAGER MESSAGE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '178-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-11 06:57:33', '2019-03-11 06:57:33', '', 178, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/178-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
