(675, 1, '2019-03-11 09:44:52', '2019-03-11 09:44:52', 'Email : anu.george@gmail.com\r\n\r\nDr. Anu George works as the Asst. Head of Department and Associate Professor at               Viswajyothi School of Management Studies, Vazhakulam since the inception of the             Department in 2009. She completed her graduation from Nirmala College for Women,        Coimbatore and MBA from GRG SMS, Bharatiyar University, Coimbatore. She went on to       teach BBM students in Nirmala College for a period of two years. Her international work     exposure was Team Leader, Cash Team of Compass Group, at the Zurich Airport, Switzerland. She went on to complete her Ph. D from University of Kerala in the area of Ecommerce and Online Shopping Behaviour. She was awarded the doctorate in the year 2012. She has         presented many papers in National and International Conferences and has won two best     paper awards.  She has authored a book on Human Resource management. She has chaired many conferences and Judges Inter college fests. Her areas of academic interest include     Management Concepts, Services Marketing, Business Communication and Human Resource Management. She has a teaching Experience of 10 Years and an Industry Experience of 3 Years.\r\n<h4><strong>Educational Qualification</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>P.hD ( Management) (University of Kerala) (2012)</li>\r\n 	<li>MBA (Bharatiyar University, Coimbatore)(1996)</li>\r\n 	<li>B.Com (Bharatiyar University, Coimbatore)(1994)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>Work Experience</strong></h4>\r\n<strong>Academics</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>1996-1998: Lecturer, Department of Management Studies, Nirmala College, Coimbatore</li>\r\n 	<li>2009-2014: Assistant Professor, Department of Management Studies, Viswajyothi College of Engineering and Technology, Vazhakulam</li>\r\n 	<li>2014-2019: Associate Professor, Department of Management Studies, Viswajyothi College of Engineering and Technology, Vazhakulam</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>