(678, 1, '2019-03-11 10:18:51', '2019-03-11 10:18:51', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Email-ID: midhunj@vjcet.org</strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Mr. Midhun Jose completed his graduate studies in Bachelor of Commerce from Newman              College Thodupuzha, Kerala. Subsequently he completed his postgraduate diploma in Mass Communication and Journalism from Madras Christian College, Chennai and MBA from Kristu Jayanti College, Bangalore. Mr. Midhun Jose is pursuing his PhD in Management studies from NIU, Thuckalay, Tamil Nadu .His proven record of ability to conduct high quality training is reflected in the students and has helped them secure prestigious placements.  He has participated in many academic seminars and workshops aimed at sharing research outcomes and building interdisciplinary collaboration within and outside the department. His contribution to the development, planning and implementation of high quality activities in the department is evident in the admissions and placements of VSMS.  Mr. Midhun’s handful experience in the industry and 10 years of teaching makes him a perfect blend for VSMS.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Educational Qualification</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Ph.D. (Management) (NIU Tamil Nadu)</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">MBA (Bangalore University)</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">PGDJMC (MCC, Chennai)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>Work Experience</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Academics</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>2010-2019 VSMS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Industry</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li> 2005-2010 via.com Bangalore</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>Areas of Interest </strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Case analysis of HR and Marketing,</li>\r\n 	<li>Placement trainings,</li>\r\n 	<li>Planning and participate in the administration of the department programs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>Publications</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<l