(986, 1, '2019-03-19 08:32:39', '2019-03-19 08:32:39', '<strong>Industrial Visit to Lunar Rubbers (Pvt) Ltd. Thodupuzha</strong>\r\n\r\nAn Industrial Visit was organized for the students of 2017-19 MBA batch on 08.08.2017 to Lunar Rubbers (Pvt) Ltd. Thodupuzha. The students, along with the faculty members, got a chance to interact with the supervisors of the various production units, and to learn about the management of the company.\r\n\r\nThe students were able to witness the product manufacturing process&nbsp;and had interactions with the employees in order to gain an idea about their experiences in the Industry.&nbsp;', 'INDUSTRY VISIT AND CONCURRENT FIELD WORK', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '281-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-19 08:32:39', '2019-03-19 08:32:39', '', 281, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/281-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
