(988, 1, '2019-03-19 08:36:17', '2019-03-19 08:36:17', '<h4><strong>Industrial Visit to Lunar Rubbers (Pvt) Ltd. Thodupuzha</strong></h4>\r\nAn Industrial Visit was organized for the students of 2017-19 MBA batch on 08.08.2017 to Lunar Rubbers (Pvt) Ltd. Thodupuzha. The students, along with the faculty members, got a chance to interact with the supervisors of the various production units, and to learn about the management of the company.\r\n\r\nThe students were able to witness the product manufacturing process&nbsp;and had interactions with the employees in order to gain an idea about their experiences in the Industry.&nbsp;', 'INDUSTRY VISIT AND CONCURRENT FIELD WORK', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '281-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-19 08:36:17', '2019-03-19 08:36:17', '', 281, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/281-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(989, 1, '2019-03-27 09:38:13', '2019-03-27 09:38:13', 'VSMS regularly conducts invited talks from various industries such as Banking, Insurance, Retailing, IT, Automobile, Steel and Energy. We also facilitate panel discussions on rising challenges in the industry with a global outlook. Apart from talks and discussion, we arrange internship opportunity to our students. Every student, after completing their first year, has to associate with a company for a period of two months. During the program, students will obtain on the job work experience and get an opportunity to conduct a research project in their area of interest. Thus, our students will get a first experience of their future job while they study at Viswajothi.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"http://www.vjcetmba.in/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/image2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1101\" src=\"http://www.vjcetmba.in/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/image2-300x225.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\"></a><a href=\"http://www.vjcetmba.in/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/industry-2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1104\" src=\"http://www.vjcetmba.in/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/industry-2-300x225.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\"></a>', 'INDUSTRY FAMILIARISATION PROGRAMME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '277-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-03-27 09:38:13', '2019-03-27 09:38:13', '', 277, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/277-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(990, 1, '2019-03-19 10:32:30', '2019-03-19 10:32:30', 'A one-day training session led by Prof. Vivek (Management Academician from Muscat) was\norganized for the Tl MBA students .The Chief Resource person conveyed to the students that\nthey should Take the road that is less travelled\', as he felt that was the key to success.\n\nThe session witnessed several team building\nactivities and problem solving activities for the\nstudents. It was a refreshing event which allowed\nstudents to take a short break from the usual\nacademic course of studies.', 'One day Training on \'Enhancing Aspirations\' by Prof. Vivek', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '71-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-03-19 10:32:30', '2019-03-19 10:32:30', '', 71, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/71-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
