(992, 1, '2019-03-19 10:36:20', '2019-03-19 10:36:20', 'The students along with faculty members Dr Geo Baby (HOD) and Mrs. Ambily Jose(Asst.Professor) attended the 60th AIMA-KMA \" Shaping Young Minds\" Programme which was conducted at CUSAT on 23rd August 2017.lt was a one day workshop consisting of several expert talks over various aspects of management, by leaders from different streams and walks of life.\n\nEach session had a moderator and a panel of students who were allowed to ask questions to the speaker. Prominent personalities like General.V.P.Malik (Former Chief of Indian Army) ,Ambassador Gurjit Singh(Former Indian Ambassador to Germany, Indonesia &amp; Ethiopia),\nDr.Sikha Nehru Sharma(MD, NutriHealth) and Chef. Sanjeev Kapoor(Celebrity Chef) gave their thoughts on how they succeeded, sharing about their own life experiences. The students were motivated and considered it as an utmost privilege for them to participate in such big events.', '60th AIMA/KMA Shaping Young Minds Program', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '67-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-03-19 10:36:20', '2019-03-19 10:36:20', '', 67, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/67-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
