(996, 1, '2019-03-19 10:39:29', '2019-03-19 10:39:29', 'Department of Management Studies VJCET conducted Bodhi 10.0 Management Fest on\r\n25th&amp; 26th of August 2017. Students from various Management Schools participated in the\r\nfest. The events were Pragyaan( Business Quiz), Prezentia (Paper Presentation), The Tycoon ( Best Manager Competition), Think Talk (Best Management Team competition).', 'BODHI 10.0 National Level Management Fest', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '64-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-19 10:39:29', '2019-03-19 10:39:29', '', 64, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/64-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(997, 1, '2019-03-19 10:48:54', '2019-03-19 10:48:54', '<h4>Airline Industry</h4>\r\nKnowledge of various industries, it\'s nature their business models etc. found to be very effective in enhancing the aspirations of young managers. AtVSMS in this series Practicing managers from different industries interact with students and enlight them with the essential details of the respective industry. Mr. Rajive Soman, Manager Revenue of Maldivian Airlines introduced the Airline industry to our MBA students. His session covered Brief History, Essentials of Airline Business, Revenue Management strategies and few case studies on Airline Industries made the session really rich and useful. Thanks to Ms. Ambily for organizing it well.', 'INDUSTRY FAMILIARISATION PROGRAMME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '277-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-19 10:48:54', '2019-03-19 10:48:54', '', 277, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/277-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
