(1077, 1, '2019-03-25 06:29:29', '2019-03-25 06:29:29', '<h4>BODHI</h4>\r\nBodhi is an inter-collegiate techno management fest of VISWAJYOTHI, which has been hosted by the college ever since its inception in 2006. Bodhi has competitive events for engineers and management students. Bodhi opens up opportunity to test the mettle with the peers in colleges all over Kerala. Foot falls for the event is kept crawling up year after year. The event is conducted over a 3 days in the month of March.\r\n<h4>DRISHYA</h4>\r\nDrishya is an annual inter-college cultural fest organized by the students of VISWAJYOTHI. Drishya blends a series of fine-arts, socio-cultural and literary events, along with a variety of workshops, exhibitions and informal events. The fest attracts thousands of visitors to the campus annually, and is one of the biggest cultural fests in central kerala.', 'COLLEGE FEST', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '299-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-25 06:29:29', '2019-03-25 06:29:29', '', 299, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/299-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1078, 1, '2019-03-25 06:32:11', '2019-03-25 06:32:11', 'VSMS offers mentoring to our students. As part of this program we keep track of the academic performance of our students and provide regular inputs to improve. Apart from this we have external agencies from industry, who have proven records in industrial training, to access the student’s managerial skill and to provide timely feedbacks to each of our students. Faculty who is in charge of a student will update the mentoring file on a regular basis and the student details are shared with parents during open house meeting.', 'Mentoring', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '269-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-25 06:32:11', '2019-03-25 06:32:11', '', 269, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/269-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1079, 1, '2019-03-25 06:32:44', '2019-03-25 06:32:44', 'VSMS is keen on adding value to its students. We provide value addition in terms of domain certification in the area of Finance, Business Analytics, IBM SPSS and Advanced Microsoft Excel. Thus, we preparer our students to be industry ready while they sit for final placements.', 'DOMAIN CERTIFICATION', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '273-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-25 06:32:44', '2019-03-25 06:32:44', '', 273, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/273-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1080, 1, '2019-03-25 06:44:17', '2019-03-25 06:44:17', 'VSMS regularly conducts invited talks from various industries such as Banking, Insurance, Retailing, IT, Automobile, Steel and Energy. We also facilitate panel discussions on rising challenges in the industry with a global outlook. Apart from talks and discussion, we arrange internship opportunity to our students. Every student, after completing their first year, has to associate with a company for a period of two months. During the program, students will obtain on the job work experience and get an opportunity to conduct a research project in their area of interest. Thus, our students will get a first experience of their future job while they study at Viswajothi.', 'INDUSTRY FAMILIARISATION PROGRAMME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '277-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-25 06:44:17', '2019-03-25 06:44:17', '', 277, 'http://intersmart.co.in/viswajyothi/277-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
