(1100, 1, '2019-03-27 08:02:49', '2019-03-27 08:02:49', 'Department of Management Studies of VISWAJYOTHI College of Engineering and Technology, popularly known as VISWAJYOTHI School of Management Studies (VSMS) is a part of the VISWAJYOTHI College of Engineering and Technology (VJCET), one of the premier self-financing Engineering Colleges of Kerala, approved by AICTE and affiliated to Kerala Technological University. The College, established in 2001, is managed by the Diocesan Technical Education Trust under the auspices of the Kothamangalam Diocese.', 'HOME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-27 08:02:49', '2019-03-27 08:02:49', '', 8, 'http://www.vjcetmba.in/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
