(1144, 1, '2019-03-29 10:07:08', '2019-03-29 10:07:08', 'VSMS is keen on adding value to its students. We provide value addition in terms of domain certification in the area of Finance, Business Analytics, IBM SPSS and Advanced Microsoft Excel. Thus, we preparer our students to be industry ready while they sit for final placements.', 'DOMAIN CERTIFICATION', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '273-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-29 10:07:08', '2019-03-29 10:07:08', '', 273, 'http://www.vjcetmba.in/273-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
