(1150, 1, '2019-03-29 10:08:06', '2019-03-29 10:08:06', 'VSMS offers mentoring to our students. As part of this program we keep track of the academic performance of our students and provide regular inputs to improve. Apart from this we have external agencies from industry, who have proven records in industrial training, to access the student’s managerial skill and to provide timely feedbacks to each of our students. Faculty who is in charge of a student will update the mentoring file on a regular basis and the student details are shared with parents during open house meeting.', 'Mentoring', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '269-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-29 10:08:06', '2019-03-29 10:08:06', '', 269, 'http://www.vjcetmba.in/269-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
